&lt;li&gt;Achieve high student start rates by leading in personal production and meeting enrollment targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other departments and&amp;nbsp;participate&amp;nbsp;in recruitment events to enhance outreach and support new students.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
